{"tid":1894794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"桑德斯：若中共侵台 美軍必定介入！","createTime":"2020-02-24T06:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T19:32:01.000Z","uid":54373,"like":61,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"025d75342c13a233cb98aed81be98f025535e716","tid":1894794,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨總統參選人桑德斯（Bernie Sanders）在接受哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）節目《60分鐘時事雜誌》（60 Minutes）訪問時，被問及如果他當選總統後中國大陸武力侵犯台灣，會否下令採取軍事行動，桑德斯給予肯定答案，說：「確實會，沒錯。我的意思是，我們必須向世界各國表明，絕不會袖手旁觀讓侵略出現。」他並指出，若他當選總統後美國人和盟友受到威脅，美國就會動武。<br />\n<br />\n另外，桑德斯表示如果當選，會與任何和美國敵對的國家領袖會面，包括朝鮮領袖金正恩，又稱美國總統特朗普先前「沒準備好」就與金正恩見面，暗示這是雙方最後一次「特金會」失敗的原因。"},{"pid":"7ec60e73e1fce3642b53f48d441c1bb4b363048b","tid":1894794,"uid":123738,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"支那從不向美帝低頭，聽日就開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先頭部隊係口交部"},{"pid":"b1e7b8dd1440cadbeac7a3be940a515591f0575a","tid":1894794,"uid":194130,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"中共既生化武器已經入侵全世界<br />\n美軍去左邊?"},{"pid":"067e119290d9d4145cd5c197b9af50576b641437","tid":1894794,"uid":19527,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"唔覺得呢啲老好人會夠中共玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cefd63177c339801c2bd1b370f584ba3e2f5229","tid":1894794,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"不惜一切同社會主義人士合作，呢個就係左派嘅真正面目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MvF_D4tVfYU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMvF_D4tVfYU&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=a17e3430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MvF_D4tVfYU</a>"},{"pid":"42b10925bf65cdf940c47caeb91001bb2ce9591a","tid":1894794,"uid":68620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"我唔信，聽日